description: Yeehaa is a seasoned professional with a diverse background in technology, innovation, and entrepreneurship. With a Master's degree in Computer Science from MIT and over 15 years of experience, Yeehaa has led major AI and cloud projects at Google and Microsoft. Founding and selling a successful ML startup highlights their strategic and leadership skills. Known for innovation and excellence, Yeehaa's work has earned several industry awards.
